name: The Cassiopeian Wanderer
description:
A fictional character that I made about a traveler in the northern sky constellation and has 3 giant creatures accompanying him, namely The Giant Flying Hahalua. 

Every aspect of this work of fiction is influenced by Greek mythology, Cultural significance of Manta Ray in Hawaii, and 'Fragile' album by YES.

Digital Drawing / JPEG / 3000x4000px / 500dpi
